329
00:18:40,083 --> 00:18:42,458
<i>No programa. Novo homem no andar.</i>

330
00:18:42,541 --> 00:18:43,583
<i>Todos mantenham as posições.</i>

331
00:18:43,708 --> 00:18:45,125
KINO: Novo homem no andar!

332
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:46,791
