365
00:22:13,375 --> 00:22:14,375
Sai!

366
00:22:17,166 --> 00:22:18,166
Kino! Vamos!

367
00:22:18,250 --> 00:22:19,250
Temos que proteger o nível!

368
00:22:19,333 --> 00:22:20,333
Outra pessoa faz isso.

369
00:22:20,791 --> 00:22:21,791
Explodam os consoles.

370
00:22:21,958 --> 00:22:23,375
